msgctxt "56"
msgid "How to Play Eight-Ball:"
msgstr "How to Play Eight-Ball:"

msgctxt "68"
msgid "Eight-Ball uses balls numbered 1 through 15."
msgstr "Eight-Ball uses balls numbered 1 through 15."

msgctxt "80"
msgid "Balls are divided into two groups: numbers 1 through 7 are considered \"Low Balls,\" while numbers 9 to 15 are considered \"High Balls.\""
msgstr "Balls are divided into two groups: numbers 1 through 7 are considered \"Low Balls,\" while numbers 9 to 15 are considered \"High Balls.\""

msgctxt "92"
msgid "The first ball that is pocketed after the break shot determines the group you will be targeting."
msgstr "The first ball that is pocketed after the break shot determines the group you will be targeting."

msgctxt "104"
msgid "To win, you must pocket the 8 ball after pocketing all of the balls in your group."
msgstr "To win, you must pocket the 8 ball after pocketing all of the balls in your group."

msgctxt "116"
msgid "As long as the balls are in your group, they can be sunk in any order."
msgstr "As long as the balls are in your group, they can be sunk in any order."

msgctxt "128"
msgid "When you're ready to pocket the 8 ball, you must specify the pocket that you'll be aiming for."
msgstr "When you're ready to pocket the 8 ball, you must specify the pocket that you'll be aiming for."

msgctxt "140"
msgid "Sinking the 8 ball into a pocket other than the one you specified results in an automatic loss."
msgstr "Sinking the 8 ball into a pocket other than the one you specified results in an automatic loss."

msgctxt "152"
msgid "Pocketing the 8 ball before all of the balls in your group have been sunk also counts as a loss."
msgstr "Pocketing the 8 ball before all of the balls in your group have been sunk also counts as a loss."

msgctxt "164"
msgid "Fouls:"
msgstr "Faltas:"

msgctxt "176"
msgid "If the cue ball falls into a pocket or does not strike an object ball, it is deemed a foul."
msgstr "Si la bola blanca cae en una de las bolsas o no pega a ninguna bola, se considera falta."

msgctxt "188"
msgid "The opposing player may then take a shot by placing the cue ball anywhere on the table."
msgstr "The opposing player may then take a shot by placing the cue ball anywhere on the table."

msgctxt "200"
msgid "Now let's try it out."
msgstr "Now let's try it out."

